      <h2>Transfer your credit or ticket to a new card online</h2>

<ol>
	<li><a href="/fares/how-to-pay-and-where-to-buy-tickets-and-oyster/buying-tickets-and-oyster">Get a new Oyster card</a></li>
	<li>Make at least one journey with it</li>
	<li>Wait 24 hours</li>
	<li>Sign in to your account, or create an account</li>
	<li>Go to 'Report card lost, stolen or failed'</li>
	<li>Select 'Transfer my products to another Oyster card' and follow the instructions</li>
</ol>
      
           
      
